What really makes Vin et Fleurs special is the owner's passion for both wine and flowers.  A former florist, he still enjoys going to the flower market to pick out his own fresh flowers and creating unique arrangements that fill the space with a feeling of warmth and elegance.  As a wine lover and connoisseur, the vast wine list reflects great selections from all over the world.  The flowers, the wine as well as the perfectly prepared American classics with a French twist make Vin et Fleurs at must see.
